comments.body:
Should the application return a 400 as well?

At one point we had put some efforts into handling this sort of request in orangelight. Look into what we did there and ask @christinach if we feel good about how it turned out.

Here's the OL solution: https://github.com/pulibrary/orangelight/blob/a24c7f08c34e0abd55ec65dec6b70ab792aebbb6/lib/orangelight/middleware/invalid_parameter_handler.rb

We look for specific patterns, presumably based on what we've seen in honeybadger.
